{"hash":"27d51839897e2eea75bca3f301effe4145576cf9","data":{"doc":{"title":"File steps","path":"/en/plugins/files/","date":"20. September 2022","content":"<p>This plugin provides steps to operate on local files and directories during test execution.\nIt is useful in end-to-end scenarios where the system creates, modifies, copies, moves, or deletes files.</p>\n<hr>\n<ul id=\"toc\">\n<li><a href=\"#install\">Install</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#options\">Options</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#filestimeout\"><code class=\"language-text\">files.timeout</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#filesenablecleanupuponcompletion\"><code class=\"language-text\">files.enableCleanupUponCompletion</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#fileslinks\"><code class=\"language-text\">files.links</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#steps\">Steps</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#define-timeout\">Define timeout</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#move-file-or-directory-to-a-directory\">Move file or directory to a directory</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#move-file-or-directory-to-a-file\">Move file or directory to a file</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#copy-file-or-directory-to-a-directory\">Copy file or directory to a directory</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#copy-file-or-directory-to-a-file\">Copy file or directory to a file</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#delete-file-or-directory\">Delete file or directory</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#wait-for-deletion\">Wait for deletion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#wait-for-modification\">Wait for modification</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#wait-for-creation\">Wait for creation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check-file-exists\">Check file exists</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check-file-does-not-exist\">Check file does not exist</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check-file-text-content\">Check file text content</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check-file-content-by-ranges\">Check file content by ranges</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check-file-length\">Check file length</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Install</h2>\n<p>Include the module in the corresponding section.</p>\n<div id=\"coord\" class=\"remark-code-tabs\"><label for=\"coord#0\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#0 name=\"coord\" checked/> yaml\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\">es.iti.wakamiti:io-wakamiti-plugin:2.7.0</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">es.iti.wakamiti:io-wakamiti-plugin:2.7.0</pre></div></div><label for=\"coord#2\" class=\"remark-code-tab\">\n                        <input type=\"radio\" id=coord#2 name=\"coord\" /> maven\n                    </label><div class=\"remark-code-content\"><div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\">&lt;dependency>\n  &lt;groupId>es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId>\n  &lt;artifactId>io-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId>\n  &lt;version>2.7.0&lt;/version>\n&lt;/dependency></pre><pre class=\"hidden\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n  &lt;groupId&gt;es.iti.wakamiti&lt;/groupId&gt;\n  &lt;artifactId&gt;io-wakamiti-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n  &lt;version&gt;2.7.0&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre></div></div></div>\n<hr class=\"remark-code-tabs-x\" rel=\"coord#maven\" />\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Options</h2>\n<h3 id=\"filestimeout\"><a href=\"#filestimeout\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">files.timeout</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">long</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code class=\"language-text\">60</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Maximum wait time in seconds for file wait steps.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">files</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">timeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">120</span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"filesenablecleanupuponcompletion\"><a href=\"#filesenablecleanupuponcompletion\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">files.enableCleanupUponCompletion</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">boolean</code></li>\n<li>Default: <code class=\"language-text\">false</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If enabled, tracked file operations are automatically cleaned up at the end of execution.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">files</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">enableCleanupUponCompletion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"fileslinks\"><a href=\"#fileslinks\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><code class=\"language-text\">files.links</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Type: <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Defines symbolic links created during setup.\nFormat: <code class=\"language-text\">source=target</code>, separated by commas or semicolons.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">files</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">links</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./tmp/incoming=./runtime/incoming; ./tmp/out=./runtime/out\"</span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"steps\"><a href=\"#steps\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Steps</h2>\n<h3 id=\"define-timeout\"><a href=\"#define-timeout\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Define timeout</h3>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><button onclick=\"copyToClipboard(this)\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-copy-icon\">\n    <path d=\"M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n      <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"clipboard-check-icon hidden\">\n    <path d=\"M13.78 4.22a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-7.25 7.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0L2.22 9.28a.751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018L6 10.94l6.72-6.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n                </button><pre class=\"language-text\">a file timeout of {value} seconds</pre><pre class=\"hidden\">a file timeout of {value} seconds</pre></div>\n<p>Declarative way to set the configuration property <a href=\"#filestimeout\"><code class=\"language-text\">files.timeout</code></a>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Parameters:</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Wakamiti type</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">value</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">long</code> <em>required</em></td>\n<td>Timeout in seconds</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"examples\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Examples:</h4>\n<div class=\"remark-code-clipboard\"><pre class=\"language-gherkin\">Given a file timeout of 120 seconds</pre></div>\n<h3 id